    {
      "id": 62,
      "name": "Sometimes you might see chapters that you didn't select showing up in searches. This is probably a result of certain words and phrases belonging to more than one chapter, and thus bridging chapters that you didn't intend. This possibility for bridging is intentional, as it allows \"lateral thinking\", which is an important source of discovery.",
      "alias": "",
      "type": "Event"
    },
    {
