    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "name": "The goal is to implement useful search patterns for a graph structure in an efficient way.",
      "alias": "",
      "type": "Event"
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "name": "The hard problem of knowledge is context.",
      "alias": "",
      "type": "Event"
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "name": "The most frequently used n-grams are the least meaningful, used for padding and rhythm",
      "alias": "",
      "type": "Thing"
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "name": "The overlap between \"+\" and \"-\" promises is the outcome. In order to make this effective, it requires some planning in the way we name sections. This is something that develops over time, so we have to understand that knowledge is individual, dynamic and interactive--a process, not a stale archive written once and for all.",
      "alias": "",
      "type": "Event"
    },
